&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;1、&lt;span style='line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 7pt; font-stretch: normal;'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;患者&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;60岁老年女&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;性。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;、既往有高血压病史10余年，血压最高200/110mmHg，间断口服降压药物治疗，平素血压值不详。脑梗死病史2年，遗留左侧肢体活动不利及言语不利。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;、主要症状：患者于&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;4小时&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;前无明显诱因突发右上肢活动不灵，无力感，活动笨拙，无意识障碍，无抽搐及二便失禁，右下肢活动不利10余天，行走时抬起困难，未重视，自行应用口服药物（具体不详）后症状无减轻，无头痛，头晕，无恶心呕吐，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;无心慌、胸闷、气短、胸痛，无腹痛腹泻，无咳嗽、咳痰，无发热寒战。于急诊行头颅CT示双侧基底节区、双侧半卵圆中心多发腔隙性脑梗死，故急诊以脑梗死收治入院。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;、查体：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;T&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;36.7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;℃&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;P&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;：80&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;次&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;分，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;R&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;：18&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;次&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;分，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;BP&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;160/100mmHg&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;，双肺未闻及啰音。心率&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;80&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;次&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;分，律齐，未闻及早搏及杂音，腹软无压痛，双下肢无指凹性水肿。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;background: white; font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background: white; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;神经系统检查：神清，言语欠流利，查体合作。额纹对称，瞳孔正大等圆，对光反射灵敏。鼻唇沟无变浅，伸舌不偏。四肢肌力V级弱，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background: white; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;肌张力正常。双侧&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.5pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt;&quot;&gt;二，三头&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 13.5pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt;&quot;&gt;肌腱反射，跟膝腱反射（+）。&lt;/span&gt;双侧巴氏征及克氏征均阴性。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;、辅助检查&lt;font face=&quot;Helvetica&quot;&gt;：2017-1-13我院行头颅CT示：双侧基底节区及双侧半卵圆中心区腔隙性脑梗死&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;